                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-4x text-muted"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="mb-3">You haven't applied for any jobs yet</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">When you apply for a job, your application will appear here for you to track.</p>
