                                                    <p>I am writing to express my interest in the Front-end Developer position at your company. With over 3 years of experience working with ReactJS and modern web technologies, I believe I can make a significant contribution to your development team.</p>
                                                    <p>Best regards,<br>Nguyen Van A</p>
